  <p>
    Wondering how to solve the <a href="../../country?country=CH&amp;redirect=%252Fblog%252Fcapture-the-flag-20">
    Capture the Flag 2.0</a> levels? Want to meet your fellow CTF solvers in
    person? This Thursday, we're hosting a meetup for the CTF challenge.
  </p>

  <p>
    The CTF organizers will present on the motivation and solutions for
    all nine levels. Beer and snacks are on us, and people of any
    technical skill level are welcome. This is a 21+ only event.
  </p>

